      <p class="text-xl">
        Since 2008, we've been Toronto's go-to basement waterproofing specialists. With over 5,000 Toronto homes protected, 
        we understand the unique challenges of Toronto's clay soil, harsh winters, and aging infrastructure. Our Toronto-focused 
        approach delivers permanent solutions tailored to your neighborhood's specific needs.
      </p>
      
      <div class="mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-center">
        <div class="bg-white/10 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">15+</div>
          <div class="text-sm">Years in Toronto</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">5,000+</div>
          <div class="text-sm">Homes Protected</div>
        </div>
