          question="Do you work during Toronto winters?"
          variant="card"
        >
          <p>Yes! Interior waterproofing works year-round regardless of weather. For exterior work, we use heated enclosures and winter-grade materials. Emergency service is available 24/7 regardless of weather conditions.</p>
